&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( hindi : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , english : madness ) is a 2002 indian psychological thriller film directed by anees bazmee . this movie is loosely based on the 1996 richard gere movie primal fear . the film stars ajay devgan , akshaye khanna and urmila matondkar in lead roles . the film premiered on 25 october 2002 . this was devgan 's first negative role .